name: 10 Eco Let Go Lanterns - Metal free design
description: New eco-lanterns are 100% biodegradable and harmless to animals if eaten. Currently only available in white, but we're working on it! They look especially good when released all together - see the video (but don't forget to click back on your browser after watching!). White pack contains: Lanterns are fire retardant and biodegradable. Lanterns measure approximately 30" high and 16" across. Watch a video of Let Go Lanterns being released
